{"word":"γυνή","slug":"γυνή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>γυνή, αιϰός, ἡ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>; in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Hom.\">Hom.</a> ‘woman’ in various occupations and social roles, and as ‘spouse’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> of any adult female <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b><i>woman</i> <a href='B:470 9:20'>Mt 9:20</a>; <a href='B:490 1:42'>Lk 1:42</a>; <a href='B:500 4:7'>J 4:7</a>; <a href='B:510 1:14'>Ac 1:14</a>; <a href='B:510 5:14'>5:14</a>; <a href='B:520 7:2'>Ro 7:2</a>; <a href='B:530 11:3'>1 Cor 11:3</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ch.\">ch.</a>; <b><a href='B:550 4:4'>Gal 4:4</a>.</b> The vocative <el>γύναι</el> <b><a href='B:470 15:28'>Mt 15:28</a>; <a href='B:490 22:57'>Lk 22:57</a>; <a href='B:500 2:4'>J 2:4</a>; <a href='B:500 19:26'>19:26</a>; <a href='B:500 20:13'>20:13</a>, <a href='B:500 20:15'>15</a></b> is sometimes, but unnecessarily, omitted in translation. <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> <i>wife</i> <a href='B:470 1:20'>Mt 1:20</a>, <a href='B:470 1:24'>24</a>; <a href='B:470 5:28'>5:28</a>, <a href='B:470 5:31'>31</a>, <a href='B:470 5:32'>32</a>; <a href='B:470 27:19'>27:19</a>; <a href='B:490 1:5'>Lk 1:5</a>; <a href='B:490 3:19'>3:19</a>; <a href='B:490 20:33'>20:33</a>; <a href='B:530 7:2'>1 Cor 7:2</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in chs. 7 and 11; <b><a href='B:560 5:22'>Eph 5:22</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ch.\">ch.</a>; <b><a href='B:580 3:18'>Col 3:18f</a>; <a href='B:610 2:9-14'>1 Ti 2:9-14</a>; <a href='B:670 3:1'>1 Pt 3:1</a>; <a href='B:730 2:20'>Rv 2:20</a>.—</b>Without specific <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to marital status<b> <a href='B:530 7:1'>1 Cor 7:1</a>.</b> —Use of γ. in <b><a href='B:500 4:1'>J 4</a></b> appears to be marked with designed ambiguity. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:γυναικεῖος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Γώγ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}